Best1BinDEBreeder
public class Rand1ExpDEBreeder
extends DEBreeder

Rand1ExpDEBreeder implements the DE/rand/1/exp Differential Evolution Algorithm, explored recently in the "Differential Evolution: A Practical Approach to Global Optimization" book by Kenneth Price, Rainer Storn, and Jouni Lampinen. The code relies (with permission from the original authors) on the DE algorithms posted at http://www.icsi.berkeley.edu/~storn/code.html . For more information on Differential Evolution, please refer to the aforementioned webpage and book.
